#: features/class-wps-feature-dark-mode.php:54
msgid "Adds an easy button at the top of your WordPress admin that lets you switch between light mode, dark mode, or automatic. Your choice is remembered every time you log in. Useful if you want WordPress in dark mode but the rest of your computer in light mode, or the other way around. Each person who uses WordPress can have their own preference."
msgstr ""

#: features/class-wps-feature-dark-mode.php:55
msgid "Add a simple button that lets you or your team members choose light or dark mode for WordPress, separate from your computer settings."
msgstr ""

