#: features/class-wps-feature-skiplinks.php:56
msgid "Adds a skip link that allows keyboard users to jump directly to the main content area, bypassing the site header and navigation. This is the most important skip link for accessibility, as it prevents users from having to tab through dozens of navigation links on every page. The link automatically detects common content IDs used by popular themes."
msgstr ""

#: features/class-wps-feature-skiplinks.php:57
msgid "Required for WCAG 2.1 Level A compliance. Without this, keyboard users must tab through all navigation on every page load. Enable to provide immediate access to page content."
msgstr ""

#: features/class-wps-feature-skiplinks.php:62
msgid "Skip to Navigation Link"
msgstr ""

#: features/class-wps-feature-skiplinks.php:63
#: features/class-wps-feature-skiplinks.php:66
msgid "Add skip link to main navigation menu."
msgstr ""

#: features/class-wps-feature-skiplinks.php:64
msgid "Adds a skip link that allows keyboard users to jump directly to the main navigation menu from the top of the page. This is useful for users who want to access navigation options without tabbing through header elements like logos, search boxes, or promotional banners. Particularly helpful on sites with complex headers."
msgstr ""

#: features/class-wps-feature-skiplinks.php:65
msgid "Helps users who want to navigate your site find the menu quickly. Especially useful on sites with complex headers containing search, login, or promotional elements before the main menu."
msgstr ""

#: features/class-wps-feature-skiplinks.php:70
msgid "Skip to Footer Link"
msgstr ""

#: features/class-wps-feature-skiplinks.php:71
#: features/class-wps-feature-skiplinks.php:74
msgid "Add skip link to footer section."
msgstr ""

#: features/class-wps-feature-skiplinks.php:72
msgid "Adds a skip link that allows keyboard users to jump directly to the footer section. This is useful for accessing footer navigation, copyright information, contact details, or legal links without scrolling through all page content. Particularly helpful on long-form content pages or when footer contains important navigation."
msgstr ""

#: features/class-wps-feature-skiplinks.php:73
msgid "Let users quickly access footer navigation, contact info, or legal links. Most useful on long-form content sites or when your footer contains secondary navigation or important information."
msgstr ""

