msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:62
msgid "Title Length Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:63
msgid "Verify title is right length for Google"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:64
msgid "Google displays titles between 50-60 characters on desktop. This check ensures your post title is in the optimal range so it displays fully in search results without being cut off or too short to stand out."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:65
msgid "Make sure your post title shows fully in Google search results."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:69
msgid "Meta Description Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:70
msgid "Verify summary text is provided"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:71
msgid "Meta descriptions are the summary text that appears under your title in Google search results. This check ensures you've written a description for your post to make people want to click on it."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:72
msgid "Create a summary that appears in search results to encourage people to click on your post."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:76
msgid "Heading Structure Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:77
msgid "Verify section titles are organized correctly"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:78
msgid "Headings should flow logically from H1 to H2 to H3, like an outline. This helps both Google and screen readers understand your content structure. Properly organized headings improve both search rankings and accessibility."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:79
msgid "Make sure your section titles are organized properly, like a good outline."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:83
msgid "Keyword Density Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:84
msgid "Verify main words appear enough times"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:85
msgid "Uses your focus keyword to check if you mention your main topic enough times throughout the post. Too few mentions means Google might not understand what your post is about. Too many repetitions looks like spam."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:86
msgid "Make sure you mention your main topic enough times for Google to notice."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:90
msgid "Content Length Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:91
msgid "Verify content is long enough"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:92
msgid "Longer posts (800+ words) typically rank better in Google. This check ensures your post is comprehensive enough to be considered an authoritative source on the topic and valuable to readers."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:93
msgid "Write enough content (800+ words) to rank well in Google search results."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:97
msgid "Internal Links Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:98
msgid "Verify links to other pages exist"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:99
msgid "Internal links help Google find your other pages and understand your site structure. Links also keep visitors on your site longer by offering related content. This check ensures you're linking to relevant pages on your own site."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:100
msgid "Link to other pages on your site to help Google and readers find more content."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:104
msgid "External Links Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:105
msgid "Verify links to other websites exist"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:106
msgid "Linking to reputable external sources shows your content is well-researched and adds credibility. Google looks for outbound links as a signal of quality content. This check ensures you're citing sources appropriately."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:107
msgid "Link to trusted external sources to back up your content and build credibility."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:111
msgid "Publish Time Suggestion"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:112
msgid "Suggest best day and time to publish"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:113
msgid "Analyzes when your audience is most active and suggests optimal publishing times. Publishing when more people are online increases views and engagement. Takes into account your audience's timezone and browsing patterns."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:114
msgid "Get suggestions for the best time to publish for maximum visibility."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:118
msgid "Readability Score"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:119
msgid "Calculate readability using Flesch-Kincaid"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:120
msgid "Analyzes your content using the Flesch-Kincaid readability formula to determine if it's easy to understand. Aims for a score that's readable by most adults (60+). Simpler language means more people can understand your content and higher engagement."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:121
msgid "Measure how easy your content is to read and understand."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:125
msgid "Empty Tags Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:126
msgid "Check for empty paragraphs and breaks"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:127
msgid "Detects empty or unnecessary HTML tags that clutter your code and waste space. Cleaning these up improves page load speed and makes the HTML cleaner and easier to maintain."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:128
msgid "Remove empty paragraphs and unnecessary spacing that wastes space and slows page load."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:132
msgid "Paragraph Length Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:133
msgid "Check if paragraphs are too long"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:134
msgid "Long paragraphs are hard to read, especially on phones. This check flags paragraphs that are too long and suggests breaking them up. Shorter paragraphs improve readability and keep readers engaged."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:135
msgid "Make sure your paragraphs aren't too long and hard to read."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:139
msgid "Sentence Length Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:140
msgid "Check if sentences are too long"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:141
msgid "Long, complex sentences are hard to understand. This check identifies sentences that are too long and suggests breaking them into shorter, punchier sentences. Shorter sentences make your writing clearer and more persuasive."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:142
msgid "Keep your sentences short and easy to understand."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:146
msgid "Passive Voice Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:147
msgid "Detect excessive passive voice usage"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:148
msgid "Passive voice (\\\"the article was written\\\") is weaker than active voice (\\\"I wrote the article\\\"). This check flags excessive passive voice and suggests rewriting in active voice. Active voice is more engaging, persuasive, and easier to understand."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:149
msgid "Use active voice instead of passive voice to make your writing stronger and clearer."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:153
msgid "Duplicate Content Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:154
msgid "Check for duplicate content on your site"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:155
msgid "Scans your site to find posts or pages with very similar content. Duplicate content confuses Google about which version to rank. This check helps you find and consolidate similar content to improve rankings."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:156
msgid "Find posts that are too similar to help Google rank your best content."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:160
msgid "Featured Image Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:161
msgid "Verify featured image is set and optimized"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:162
msgid "A good featured image makes your post stand out in search results and social media. This check ensures you have a featured image set and that it's the right size and format for best performance and appearance."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:163
msgid "Add an eye-catching featured image to make your post stand out on social media."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:167
msgid "Image Optimization Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:168
msgid "Check if images are compressed and optimized"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:169
msgid "Large, unoptimized images slow down your page. This check verifies images are compressed and in the right format (WEBP is better than JPEG). Optimized images load faster, improve user experience, and help your rankings."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:170
msgid "Make sure your images are compressed to load faster and improve site speed."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:174
msgid "Image Filename Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:175
msgid "Check if image filenames are descriptive"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:176
msgid "Google can't see images, but it can read the filename. Using descriptive filenames (like \\\"apple-pie-recipe.jpg\\\" instead of \\\"IMG_1234.jpg\\\") helps Google understand what the image shows and can improve rankings in image search."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:177
msgid "Name your image files descriptively so Google understands what they show."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:181
msgid "Image Alt Text Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:182
msgid "Check if all images have alt text"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:183
msgid "Alt text describes images for people using screen readers and helps Google understand images. Every image should have descriptive alt text. It's both good for accessibility and SEO - a win-win for your site."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:184
msgid "Add descriptions to all images so everyone can understand what they show."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:188
msgid "Video Embeds Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:189
msgid "Validate video embeds and URLs"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:190
msgid "Videos increase engagement and time on page, which improves rankings. This check validates that embedded videos are working properly and that video URLs are valid. Broken videos hurt user experience and rankings."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:191
msgid "Make sure embedded videos are working properly for better engagement."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:195
msgid "Categories Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:196
msgid "Check if at least one category is assigned"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:197
msgid "Categories organize your content and help Google understand your site structure. Every post should belong to at least one category. This helps both visitors and search engines navigate your site."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:198
msgid "Organize your post into categories so visitors can find related content."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:202
msgid "Tags Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:203
msgid "Check if tags are assigned"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:204
msgid "Tags are like labels that describe your post topic. While optional, tags help organize content and create topic pages that improve navigation. Using 3-5 relevant tags per post is a good practice."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:205
msgid "Add tags to help organize your content by topic."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:209
msgid "Manual Excerpt Check"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:210
msgid "Check if manual excerpt is provided"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-content-optimizer.php:211
msgid "Excerpts are summaries that appear in archives and on the homepage. Writing a custom excerpt gives you control over what preview text people see instead of WordPress automatically truncating your content."
