msgid "Remove block bindings connection code"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-interactivity-cleanup.php:32
msgid "Disables block bindings, a WordPress feature that allows blocks to dynamically connect to data sources. This is an advanced feature used by developers to build dynamic content blocks. Most sites don't use this feature. Disabling removes unnecessary code that loads even when not used."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-interactivity-cleanup.php:33
msgid "Advanced block feature for dynamic content connections. Safe to disable unless you specifically use block bindings in your theme or content."
