msgid "Record who logs in with magic links"
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-magic-link-support.php:25
msgid "Keeps detailed logs of every developer who uses a magic link to access your site, including when they logged in, how long they stayed, and what actions they took. This creates an audit trail for security purposes and helps you monitor who has access to your site. Essential for compliance and security tracking."
msgstr ""

#: includes/features/class-wps-feature-magic-link-support.php:26
msgid "Track who accessed your site via magic link. Essential for security audits and compliance. Highly recommended to keep enabled."
